This is a gift from the brand, not a paid collaboration, the video features my genuine, organic reaction.

The product feels truly relaxing to use, thanks to its vibration mode. As for the hair growth claims through LED light therapy, I’ll need more time to give a proper verdict, I’ve only used it 2-3 times so far.

According to the brand, it has shown a 98% increase in hair growth and a 67% decrease in hair fall, and it’s India’s first and only clinically tested hair growth comb.

Overall, I’m genuinely happy to see Indian brands coming up with such innovative products that are easily accessible to Indian audiences ✨
Save it now! Cause you don’t want droopy eyes!
